# Project: Vins de Loire Sponsored Landing Page

## What this is
A sponsored editorial landing page for Vins de Loire (InterLoire), hosted on a
Wine Spectator domain. Wine Spectator is the publisher; Vins de Loire is the
paying sponsor. The page showcases recent Wine Spectator scores/ratings for
Loire Valley wines, framed in WS editorial style with Vins de Loire branding.

## Stack
- Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Deployed to Vercel
- Static/SSG where possible (it's a marketing landing page)

## Design intent
- Cinematic, editorial, premium. Generous whitespace, large imagery, refined type.
- Respect the Vins de Loire / InterLoire brand book: public/brand/GS GI 0203 - INTERLOIRE BrandBook V6.pdf
  (colors, logo clear space, typography). Pull exact hex values and fonts from it.
- This is a co-branded page: Wine Spectator editorial authority + Vins de Loire identity.

## Rules
- All copy comes from src/content/CONTENT_SOURCE.docx. Do not invent marketing copy.
- All images live in public/images, logos in public/logos. Use real filenames.
- Mobile-first responsive. Test at 375px, 768px, 1440px.
- Accessible: alt text on all images, semantic HTML, proper heading order.
- No em dashes in any copy or comments. Use commas, colons, parentheses, or separate sentences.
